fields.Name: Skip AssociationDB - Top 10 Most Engaged Members
fields.Description: Tests Skip's ability to aggregate engagement across multiple domains (events, courses, chapters) and rank members.

InputDefinition.userMessage: Who are our top 10 most engaged members based on their event attendance, course enrollments, and chapter participation? Show this as a ranked table with their engagement metrics.

judgeValidationCriteria: Response includes a table showing top 10 members
Engagement metrics from multiple domains are shown (events, courses, chapters)
Members are properly ranked by overall engagement
Table is clear and easy to interpret
